Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.74,0:01:04.37,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\bord0\blur0.6\4a&HFF&\c&H30C3F1&}И {\c&HFFFFFF&}теперь {\c&H30C3F1&}мы {\c&HFFFFFF&}с {\c&H30C3F1&}тобой {\c&HFFFFFF&}ищем {\c&H30C3F1&}друг {\c&HFFFFFF&}друга
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:06.04,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6\c&H000000&}Спасу тебя
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.74,0:01:06.04,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\bord0\blur0.6\4a&HFF&\c&H30C3F1&}Спасу {\c&HFFFFFF&}тебя
